curtains opening to reveal city and falling stars.
animation 2
menu border falls down, and offers the player four options: Start New Game, Load Saved Game, Play Story, Choose Languadge.
animation 3-1

The princess' room appear, and ask the player to choose the character's skin tone, hairdress, make-up, dress, shoes, and accessory (all of them with preset options). Once the players clicks OK, he is asked if he wishes to view the History.
animation 3-2
A series of game datas are shown, containing the princess' name, thumbnail, date of last gaming, number of day's played and glamour points colected.
animation 3-3
A slideshow tells the story of the princess' debuting and thus her desire to attend to balls. It explains that she has to dress uniquely and keep clean to impress the royalty.
animation 3-4
On the same screen the flags appear. While selcting one, random phrases on that language are spoken ("good day", "bon jour.", "hola", "beinvenue", "time for the ball" and so forth) .
Game Start
From her house on Bathhouse Street. If the game was just created, then tips are on and should be disabled on pause screen.
